    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# AI-Powered Recruitment Assistant Workflow\n\n## 1. Candidate Application Intake\n\nApplications are automatically collected through multiple channels, including web forms and email submissions. Candidate resumes and profile information are captured and stored for further processing.\n\n## 2. Automated Resume Analysis\n\nThe AI engine extracts and evaluates candidate information, including:\n\n* Personal Information\n* Educational Qualifications\n* Technical Skills\n* Professional Experience\n* Project Portfolio\n* Certifications and Achievements\n\nA structured candidate profile is generated for standardized evaluation.\n\n## 3. Intelligent Candidate Screening\n\nEach candidate is assessed against the relevant Job Description (JD) using predefined screening criteria:\n\n* Technical Skills Match\n* Experience Alignment\n* Project Relevance\n* Educational Qualification Match\n\nAn AI-generated suitability score is calculated to determine candidate fit.\n\n### Screening Decision Rules\n\n* **Score ≥ 70:** Shortlisted for Technical Interview\n* **Score 50–69:** Review Required (Maybe)\n* **Score < 50:** Archived / Rejected\n\n## 4. Candidate Tracking & Record Management\n\nAll candidate records, screening outcomes, resumes, and evaluation reports are automatically stored in centralized cloud storage and logged within the Applicant Tracking System (ATS).\n\n## 5. Hiring Team Notification\n\nFor shortlisted candidates, automated notifications are sent to recruiters and hiring managers. Candidate details, evaluation summaries, and screening scores are included to support interview scheduling and decision-making.\n\n## 6. Technical Interview Preparation\n\nFor qualified candidates, the system automatically generates role-specific technical interview questions based on:\n\n* Resume Content\n* Skills Assessment\n* Job Requirements\n* Project Experience\n\n## 7. Recruitment Analytics & Reporting\n\nThe platform maintains a complete audit trail of applications, screening decisions, interview recommendations, and hiring outcomes to support recruitment analytics and performance tracking.\n",
        "height": 1200,
        "width": 976
